<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Applicants</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .summary-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .summary-number {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .summary-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
        }
        .job-list {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .job-item {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .job-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
        }
        .job-applicants {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #e9ecef;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>📬 New Job Applications</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{employerName}},</p>
            
            <p>Great news! You have received new applications for your job postings.</p>
            
            <div class="summary-box">
                <p class="summary-number">{{totalNewApplicants}}</p>
                <p class="summary-text">new {{#if (eq totalNewApplicants 1)}}applicant{{else}}applicants{{/if}} since your last notification</p>
            </div>

            {{#if jobs}}
            <div class="job-list">
                <h3 style="color: #333; font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Applications by Job:</h3>
                {{#each jobs}}
                <div class="job-item">
                    <p class="job-title">{{this.jobTitle}}</p>
                    <p class="job-applicants">{{this.newApplicants}} new {{#if (eq this.newApplicants 1)}}applicant{{else}}applicants{{/if}}</p>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">View All Applications</a>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px;">
                You're receiving this email because you have active job postings on JobTowners. We check for new applications every few hours and send you a summary when there are new applicants.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© {{year}} JobTowners. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated notification email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
